import React from "react";
import { Footer, FooterTab, Button, Text } from "native-base";
import { Link } from "react-router-native";

export const AppFooter = () => (
  <Footer>
    <FooterTab>
      <Button>
        <Link to={`/allCities`} underlayColor="#f0f4f7">
          <Text>All Cities</Text>
        </Link>
      </Button>
      <Button>
        <Link to={`/`} underlayColor="#f0f4f7">
          <Text>Home</Text>
        </Link>
      </Button>
      <Button>
        <Link to={`/starScreen`} underlayColor="#f0f4f7">
          <Text>Star</Text>
        </Link>
      </Button>
    </FooterTab>
  </Footer>
);
